The,PBS,Universal,User,Authentication,UUA,API,provides,developers,with,a,system,that,allows,for,secure,creation,and,management,of,user,accounts,withing,their,application,Once,user,accounts,are,created,the,PBS,UUA,API,exposes,RESTful,methods,for,accessing,and,modifying,information,about,authenticated,users,within,the,application,Access,to,this,API,is,only,granted,on,a,case,by,case,basis,and,only,where,other,methods,of,accessing,and,modifying,user,information,will,not,work,for,example,on,new,platforms,or,devices,which,do,not,support,standards,compliant,user,services